</ul>
<h3>&nbsp;Chinese Massage: Harmony and Healing</h3>
<p>Chinese massage, often referred to as <em>Tui Na</em>, is a cornerstone of Traditional Chinese Medicine. It uses rhythmic pressure and manipulation of meridians to restore harmony in the body. <strong>Commonly noted benefits include:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Relief from muscle tension and pain</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Better blood circulation</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Support for overall wellness and balance</p>
</li>
</ul>
